Ben: We went to the beach on Sunday.
Emma: Did you swim in the sea?
Ben: Yes, and we built a big sandcastle.
Emma: How big was it?
Ben: It was taller than my little brother!
Emma: Did you find any shells?
Ben: Yes, we collected many shells.
Emma: Did the waves break your castle?
Ben: Yes, but we laughed and built another one.
Emma: The beach is the best place in summer!
